{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "bookName": "2 Nephi",
  "chapter": 5,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "iJpuSZDxZSBJHFSeavba",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "sister-m"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 515.206,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 6.641,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, it came to pass that I, Nephi, did cry much unto the Lord my God,",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 6.821,
      "end": 9.097,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the anger of my brethren.",
      "verse": "5:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 9.777,
      "end": 13.585,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, their anger did increase against me,",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 13.765,
      "end": 17.527,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that they did seek to take away my life.",
      "verse": "5:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 18.207,
      "end": 21.04,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, they did murmur against me, saying:",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 21.22,
      "end": 24.657,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Our younger brother thinks to rule over us;",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 24.837,
      "end": 28.181,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we have had much trial because of him;",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 28.361,
      "end": 30.869,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, now let us slay him,",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 31.049,
      "end": 34.625,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that we may not be afflicted more because of his words.",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 34.805,
      "end": 38.567,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, we will not have him to be our ruler;",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 38.747,
      "end": 42.834,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for it belongs unto us, who are the elder brethren,",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 43.014,
      "end": 45.057,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to rule over this people.",
      "verse": "5:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 45.737,
      "end": 51.774,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now I do not write upon these plates all the words which they murmured against me.",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 51.954,
      "end": 56.691,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But it sufficeth me to say that they did seek to take away my life.",
      "verse": "5:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 57.371,
      "end": 64.709,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the Lord did warn me,",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 64.889,
      "end": 67.722,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I, Nephi, should depart from them",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 67.902,
      "end": 70.27,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and flee into the wilderness,",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 70.45,
      "end": 73.051,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all those who would go with me.",
      "verse": "5:5",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 73.731,
      "end": 78.7,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, it came to pass that I, Nephi, did take my family,",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 78.88,
      "end": 81.527,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also Zoram and his family,",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 81.707,
      "end": 85.701,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and Sam, mine elder brother and his family,",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 85.881,
      "end": 89.503,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and Jacob and Joseph, my younger brethren,",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 89.683,
      "end": 92.005,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also my sisters,",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 92.185,
      "end": 94.786,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all those who would go with me.",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 94.966,
      "end": 98.263,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And all those who would go with me were those",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 98.443,
      "end": 102.019,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who believed in the warnings and the revelations of God;",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 102.199,
      "end": 105.589,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they did hearken unto my words.",
      "verse": "5:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 106.269,
      "end": 108.173,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we did take our tents",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 108.353,
      "end": 111.418,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and whatsoever things were possible for us,",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 111.598,
      "end": 115.963,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did journey in the wilderness for the space of many days.",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 116.143,
      "end": 119.951,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after we had journeyed for the space of many days",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 120.131,
      "end": 121.617,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we did pitch our tents.",
      "verse": "5:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 122.297,
      "end": 127.545,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And my people would that we should call the name of the place Nephi;",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 127.725,
      "end": 130.697,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, we did call it Nephi.",
      "verse": "5:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 131.377,
      "end": 134.906,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And all those who were with me did take upon them",
      "verse": "5:9",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 135.086,
      "end": 138.012,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to call themselves the people of Nephi.",
      "verse": "5:9",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 138.692,
      "end": 141.339,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we did observe to keep the judgments,",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 141.519,
      "end": 142.959,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the statutes,",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 143.139,
      "end": 149.269,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the commandments of the Lord",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 149.449,
      "end": 153.164,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in all things, according to the law of Moses.",
      "verse": "5:10",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 153.844,
      "end": 155.748,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord was with us;",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 155.928,
      "end": 158.436,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we did prosper exceedingly;",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 158.616,
      "end": 160.381,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for we did sow seed,",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 160.561,
      "end": 163.255,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we did reap again in abundance.",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 163.435,
      "end": 169.054,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we began to raise flocks, and herds, and animals of every kind.",
      "verse": "5:11",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 169.734,
      "end": 174.378,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, had also brought the records",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 174.558,
      "end": 177.855,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were engraven upon the plates of brass;",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 178.035,
      "end": 180.125,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the ball,",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 180.305,
      "end": 181.42,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or compass,",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 181.6,
      "end": 185.176,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which was prepared for my father by the hand of the Lord,",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 185.356,
      "end": 187.539,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to that which is written.",
      "verse": "5:12",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 188.219,
      "end": 192.724,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we began to prosper exceedingly,",
      "verse": "5:13",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 192.904,
      "end": 195.04,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to multiply in the land.",
      "verse": "5:13",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 195.72,
      "end": 199.76,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, did take the sword of Laban,",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 199.94,
      "end": 203.795,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after the manner of it did make many swords,",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 203.975,
      "end": 208.294,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "lest by any means the people who were now called Lamanites",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 208.474,
      "end": 211.075,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should come upon us and destroy us;",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 211.255,
      "end": 215.202,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I knew their hatred towards me and my children",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 215.382,
      "end": 218.168,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and those who were called my people.",
      "verse": "5:14",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 218.848,
      "end": 221.959,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I did teach my people to build buildings,",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 222.139,
      "end": 227.155,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to work in all manner of wood, and of iron, and of copper,",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 227.335,
      "end": 230.679,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and of brass, and of steel, and of gold,",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 230.859,
      "end": 233.831,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and of silver, and of precious ores,",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 234.011,
      "end": 236.008,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were in great abundance.",
      "verse": "5:15",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 236.688,
      "end": 239.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, did build a temple;",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 239.84,
      "end": 244.623,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I did construct it after the manner of the temple of Solomon",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 244.803,
      "end": 248.565,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save it were not built of so many precious things;",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 248.745,
      "end": 251.856,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they were not to be found upon the land,",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 252.036,
      "end": 256.123,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, it could not be built like unto Solomon's temple.",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 256.303,
      "end": 261.179,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But the manner of the construction was like unto the temple of Solomon;",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 261.359,
      "end": 264.888,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the workmanship thereof was exceedingly fine.",
      "verse": "5:16",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 265.568,
      "end": 271.373,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, did cause my people to be industrious,",
      "verse": "5:17",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 271.553,
      "end": 273.736,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to labor with their hands.",
      "verse": "5:17",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 274.416,
      "end": 278.921,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that they would that I should be their king.",
      "verse": "5:18",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 279.101,
      "end": 284.442,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But I, Nephi, was desirous that they should have no king;",
      "verse": "5:18",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 284.622,
      "end": 290.009,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, I did for them according to that which was in my power.",
      "verse": "5:18",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 290.689,
      "end": 295.89,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, the words of the Lord had been fulfilled unto my brethren,",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 296.07,
      "end": 298.346,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he spake concerning them",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 298.526,
      "end": 301.916,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I should be their ruler and their teacher.",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 302.096,
      "end": 305.672,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I had been their ruler and their teacher,",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 305.852,
      "end": 308.592,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the commandments of the Lord,",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 308.772,
      "end": 312.58,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until the time they sought to take away my life.",
      "verse": "5:19",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 313.26,
      "end": 316.65,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, the word of the Lord was fulfilled",
      "verse": "5:20",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 316.83,
      "end": 319.291,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he spake unto me, saying that:",
      "verse": "5:20",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 319.471,
      "end": 322.954,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Inasmuch as they will not hearken unto thy words",
      "verse": "5:20",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 323.134,
      "end": 326.524,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be cut off from the presence of the Lord.",
      "verse": "5:20",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 326.704,
      "end": 330.233,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, they were cut off from his presence.",
      "verse": "5:20",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 330.913,
      "end": 334.164,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he had caused the cursing to come upon them,",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 334.344,
      "end": 336.666,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even a sore cursing,",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 336.846,
      "end": 339.122,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of their iniquity.",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 339.302,
      "end": 343.249,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, they had hardened their hearts against him,",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 343.429,
      "end": 345.937,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they had become like unto a flint;",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 346.117,
      "end": 348.393,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, as they were white,",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 348.573,
      "end": 351.452,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and exceedingly fair and delightsome,",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 351.632,
      "end": 366.771,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they might not be enticing unto my people",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 366.951,
      "end": 371.595,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord God did cause a skin of blackness to come upon them.",
      "verse": "5:21",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 372.275,
      "end": 374.458,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thus saith the Lord God:",
      "verse": "5:22",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 374.638,
      "end": 378.214,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will cause that they shall be loathsome unto thy people,",
      "verse": "5:22",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 378.394,
      "end": 381.784,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save they shall repent of their iniquities.",
      "verse": "5:22",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 382.464,
      "end": 385.436,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And cursed shall be the seed of him",
      "verse": "5:23",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 385.616,
      "end": 387.938,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that mixeth with their seed;",
      "verse": "5:23",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 388.118,
      "end": 391.926,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they shall be cursed even with the same cursing.",
      "verse": "5:23",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 392.106,
      "end": 395.45,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord spake it, and it was done.",
      "verse": "5:23",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 396.13,
      "end": 399.241,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And because of their cursing which was upon them",
      "verse": "5:24",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 399.421,
      "end": 401.929,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they did become an idle people,",
      "verse": "5:24",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 402.109,
      "end": 404.477,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "full of mischief and subtlety,",
      "verse": "5:24",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 404.657,
      "end": 408.604,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did seek in the wilderness for beasts of prey.",
      "verse": "5:24",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 409.284,
      "end": 411.374,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord God said unto me:",
      "verse": "5:25",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 411.554,
      "end": 413.969,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "They shall be a scourge unto thy seed,",
      "verse": "5:25",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 414.149,
      "end": 417.075,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to stir them up in remembrance of me;",
      "verse": "5:25",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 417.255,
      "end": 420.413,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and inasmuch as they will not remember me,",
      "verse": "5:25",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 420.593,
      "end": 423.054,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and hearken unto my words,",
      "verse": "5:25",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 423.234,
      "end": 426.485,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall scourge them even unto destruction.",
      "verse": "5:25",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 427.165,
      "end": 432.924,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, did consecrate Jacob and Joseph,",
      "verse": "5:26",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 433.104,
      "end": 437.748,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they should be priests and teachers over the land of my people.",
      "verse": "5:26",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 438.428,
      "end": 442.747,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we lived after the manner of happiness.",
      "verse": "5:27",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 443.427,
      "end": 448.675,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thirty years had passed away from the time we left Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "5:28",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 449.355,
      "end": 452.931,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, had kept the records",
      "verse": "5:29",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 453.111,
      "end": 457.291,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon my plates, which I had made, of my people thus far.",
      "verse": "5:29",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 457.971,
      "end": 461.686,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the Lord God said unto me:",
      "verse": "5:30",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 461.866,
      "end": 463.352,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Make other plates;",
      "verse": "5:30",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 463.532,
      "end": 466.922,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thou shalt engraven many things upon them",
      "verse": "5:30",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 467.102,
      "end": 469.285,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are good in my sight,",
      "verse": "5:30",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 469.465,
      "end": 471.694,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the profit of thy people.",
      "verse": "5:30",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 472.374,
      "end": 474.696,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I, Nephi,",
      "verse": "5:31",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 474.876,
      "end": 477.895,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to be obedient to the commandments of the Lord,",
      "verse": "5:31",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 478.075,
      "end": 482.533,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "went and made these plates upon which I have engraven these things.",
      "verse": "5:31",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 483.213,
      "end": 487.021,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I engraved that which is pleasing unto God.",
      "verse": "5:32",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 487.201,
      "end": 490.545,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if my people are pleased with the things of God",
      "verse": "5:32",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 490.725,
      "end": 495.044,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they will be pleased with mine engravings which are upon these plates.",
      "verse": "5:32",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 495.724,
      "end": 501.297,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if my people desire to know the more particular part of the history of my people",
      "verse": "5:33",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 501.477,
      "end": 504.31,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they must search mine other plates.",
      "verse": "5:33",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 504.99,
      "end": 509.727,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it sufficeth me to say that forty years had passed away,",
      "verse": "5:34",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 509.907,
      "end": 514.551,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we had already had wars and contentions with our brethren.",
      "verse": "5:34",
      "lineIndex": 137
    }
  ]
}